{"tid":1323224,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非要明白點解有人打狗","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T10:33:49.000Z","uid":173326,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7234cbf73a6ff93f3f658b0ef240bbb7f2524093","tid":1323224,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"係因為啲狗咬住人，咬到入商場。在場市民為左救人，先迫於無奈打兩下等隻狗鬆口。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人想虐畜，但人命關天，而且俾狗拗斷手腕/插盲眼就殘廢一世。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當俾狗咬嘅人一腳伸開隻狗，點解其他人反而鬧個傷者暴力對待動物，而唔係鬧隻狗/狗主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講緊動物"},{"pid":"0bb25030292cfb857ac9f5a842dc5c3136db4a04","tid":1323224,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7c39aa62b034caa506c57f0b60b4c9cdb8cffaeb","tid":1323224,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"如果俾幾隻狗咬個個係和理非自己嘅老豆/老母/女朋友/親生仔，唔知和理非係咪一樣用愛與和平勸止啲狗"},{"pid":"beb385baa4c6b0d4a98c9918c3fb5f4ed2de6d76","tid":1323224,"uid":761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:49:03.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a>"},{"pid":"661dafebdfe7c4f866eca26ca4917d9aa846f7f6","tid":1323224,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beb385baa4c6b0d4a98c9918c3fb5f4ed2de6d76","tid":1323224,"uid":761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:49:03.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:51:41.000Z","msg":"有部分和理非真係誤墮愛狗力嘅歪論，一度動搖過，必須提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30c5376d1775a397ff677c5098135f6eb94faf8","tid":1323224,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:33:49.000Z","msg":"就嚟入黑，注意野狗出沒<br />\n200萬人上山，就200萬人落山，一個都不能少，唔可以俾野狗叼走任何同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊行山遇到野狗"}]}